<BaseLayout
  title="Success Story: 140 St Georges Terrace — 50 Years | Landmark Anniversary Event | Bloom'n Events Co"
  description="How Bloom'n Events Co crafted and delivered a bespoke 50th Birthday Celebration for 140 St Georges Terrace, honouring the building's legacy while presenting it as contemporary and future-focused."
  path="/case-study-centuria-50th-birthday"
>
  <h1 class="visually-hidden">Success Story: 140 St Georges Terrace — 50 Years</h1>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero-section" aria-label="Hero">
    <div class="hero-background">
      <OptimizedImage
        src="/assets/images/Centuria 50th Birthday/25d854af-18a7-46ed-9cb8-1e3d7a818715.jpg"
        alt="Elegant 50th birthday celebration"
        class="hero-image"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
        decoding="async"
        sizes="100vw"
        width="1600"
        height="900"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true" />
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl px-4 text-center md:px-6">
        <h1 class="hero-headline">
          140 St Georges Terrace — 50 Years
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subhead">
          A landmark anniversary event that honoured legacy and looked forward.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-subhead">
          How Bloom'n Events Co crafted a bespoke 50th Birthday celebration that transformed shared building spaces into an elegant, welcoming environment
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Anchor nav -->
  <AnchorNav
    links={[
      { href: "#overviewHeading", label: "Overview" },
      { href: "#ourRoleHeading", label: "Our Role" },
      { href: "#producedHeading", label: "What We Produced" },
      { href: "#outcomeHeading", label: "Outcome" },
      { href: "#testimonialsHeading", label: "Testimonials" },
    ]}
    client:idle
  />

  <!-- Success Story Content -->
  <section class="section-main">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-6">
      <!-- Overview -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="overviewHeading">
        <h2 id="overviewHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-charcoal mb-3">To celebrate the 50th anniversary of 140 St Georges Terrace, Centuria invited Bloom'n Events Co. to conceive and deliver a <strong>multi-layered landmark celebration</strong>—one that honoured the building's past, activated the present, and confidently signalled its future.</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal mb-0">This was not a single-night event, but a <strong>month-long placemaking and storytelling experience</strong>, culminating in a high-profile civic celebration within a live, operational commercial building.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Our Role -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="ourRoleHeading">
        <h2 id="ourRoleHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Our Role</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-charcoal mb-3">Bloom'n Events Co. was entrusted as <strong>lead creative producer</strong>, responsible for:</p>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Creative direction and narrative development</li>
              <li>Graphic design of all event assets, imagery, and displays</li>
              <li>Custom fabrication and installation</li>
              <li>Subcontractor and talent coordination</li>
              <li>Speaker management, speechwriting, and protocol</li>
              <li>End-to-end delivery and onsite execution</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal mt-3 mb-0">Every touchpoint—from foyer installations to hospitality details—was intentionally designed, produced, and managed in-house or through curated specialist partners.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What We Produced & Delivered -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="producedHeading">
        <h2 id="producedHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">What We Produced & Delivered</h2>
        
        <!-- Creative Concept & Narrative -->
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="text-gold mb-3">Creative Concept & Narrative</h3>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Developed a <em>"Building Through the Ages"</em> storytelling framework</li>
              <li>Designed the event journey to build toward a future-facing reveal moment</li>
              <li>Ensured all elements aligned with Centuria's brand, tone, and asset positioning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Graphic Design & Visual Storytelling -->
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="text-gold mb-3">Graphic Design & Visual Storytelling</h3>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Designed <strong>all graphic assets</strong>, including historical displays, large-format decals, signage, and printed collateral</li>
              <li>Created <strong>8-metre-tall pillar decals</strong> illustrating the building's evolution across five decades</li>
              <li>Designed and installed a <strong>giant celebration decal</strong> marking the milestone</li>
              <li>Produced wayfinding and interpretive displays integrated seamlessly into the foyer environment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Historical Research & Content Development -->
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="text-gold mb-3">Historical Research & Content Development</h3>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Conducted detailed research into the building's role in Perth's commercial and civic history</li>
              <li>Sourced archival imagery from photographers, media archives, and private collections</li>
              <li>Managed image licensing, usage rights, and attribution</li>
              <li>Designed and produced <strong>custom history boards</strong>, connecting tenants and visitors to the building's legacy and its place in the city</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Celebration Centrepiece & Placemaking -->
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="text-gold mb-3">Celebration Centrepiece & Placemaking</h3>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Designed and <strong>hand-crafted a large-scale celebration centrepiece</strong> installed weeks prior to the event</li>
              <li>Featured oversized custom roses (400–800mm diameter) arranged around a <strong>bespoke illuminated "50"</strong>, hand-made at 900mm high in a vintage-inspired style</li>
              <li>Served as the focal point of the foyer throughout the lead-up period, creating anticipation and sustained engagement</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal mt-3 mb-0">This installation, combined with the history displays and decals, transformed the foyer into a living exhibition for the duration of the celebration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Hospitality, Styling & Experience -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="hospitalityHeading">
        <h2 id="hospitalityHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Hospitality, Styling & Experience</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Designed and <strong>hand-built custom bars</strong>, complete with bespoke event signage</li>
              <li>Developed <strong>signature anniversary cocktails</strong> aligned to the celebration theme</li>
              <li>Supplied <strong>custom event-themed cups</strong> for the resident café—available for the <em>entire month</em> of the anniversary, extending the experience into daily tenant life</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Ceremony, Talent & Programming -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="ceremonyHeading">
        <h2 id="ceremonyHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Ceremony, Talent & Programming</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Secured and coordinated a <strong>local radio personality and celebrity MC</strong></li>
              <li>Arranged the attendance and keynote address of the <strong>Lord Mayor of Perth</strong></li>
              <li>Engaged and managed a <strong>live band</strong>, providing atmosphere and energy throughout the celebration</li>
              <li>Wrote speeches for all speakers, ensuring narrative consistency, tone alignment, and smooth program flow</li>
              <li>Developed the full run sheet and managed live cueing and protocol</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Hero Moment -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="heroMomentHeading">
        <h2 id="heroMomentHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Hero Moment</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Commissioned a <strong>giant custom cake</strong>, crafted as a replica of the building</li>
              <li>Timed the cake reveal to coincide with the <strong>official unveiling of the building's new name</strong>, delivering a highly memorable and symbolic moment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Subcontractor & Stakeholder Coordination -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="subcontractorHeading">
        <h2 id="subcontractorHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Subcontractor & Stakeholder Coordination</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Managed all specialist subcontractors including fabrication, print, florals, AV, catering support, talent, and logistics</li>
              <li>Coordinated bump-in, installation, live event delivery, and pack-down within a high-traffic CBD environment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Additional Elements -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="additionalHeading">
        <h2 id="additionalHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Additional Elements (Scoped, Not Taken Up)</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Media pack and press release development</li>
              <li>Commemorative photo books documenting the building's history and celebration</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal mt-3 mb-0">These were envisioned as optional legacy extensions to the core celebration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Visual Evidence -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="visualEvidenceHeading">
        <h2 id="visualEvidenceHeading" class="heading-blush-bg text-center mb-4">Visual Evidence</h2>
        <div style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
          <Carousel slides={visualEvidenceSlides} virtualizeThreshold={8} renderWindow={5} client:visible />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The Outcome -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="outcomeHeading">
        <h2 id="outcomeHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">The Outcome</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-charcoal mb-3">The 50th Birthday celebration delivered strong engagement, positive feedback, and lasting impact:</p>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>The building's history was made tangible and accessible</li>
              <li>Tenants and stakeholders experienced a renewed sense of pride and connection</li>
              <li>The name change reveal landed with clarity and authority</li>
              <li>Centuria's custodianship of the asset was visibly reinforced</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-charcoal mt-3 mb-0">140 St Georges Terrace was celebrated not just as a landmark—but as a living part of Perth's future.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Capability Highlight -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="capabilityHeading">
        <h2 id="capabilityHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Capability Highlight</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-charcoal mb-0">This project shows Bloom'n Events Co.'s strength in delivering <strong>high-complexity, design-led corporate and civic celebrations</strong>, where storytelling, fabrication, protocol, and precision execution must operate seamlessly together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Services Delivered -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="servicesHeading">
        <h2 id="servicesHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">Services Delivered</h2>
        <div class="card mb-4" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-charcoal mb-3">End-to-end services delivered in partnership with the client to support existing relationships and in-house capabilities:</p>
            <ul class="text-charcoal mb-0 pl-4 md:pl-[120px] columns-1 md:columns-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
              <li>Creative direction</li>
              <li>Graphic design</li>
              <li>Historical research & licensing</li>
              <li>Large-format print & decals</li>
              <li>Custom fabrication</li>
              <li>Floral installations</li>
              <li>Hospitality & bar design</li>
              <li>Talent & speaker management</li>
              <li>Speechwriting</li>
              <li>Subcontractor coordination</li>
              <li>Event delivery</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <section class="mb-5 testimonials" aria-labelledby="testimonialsHeading">
        <h2 id="testimonialsHeading" class="heading-blush-bg mb-4">What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <TestimonialsCarousel client:visible />
      </section>

      <!-- Related Services -->
      <section class="mb-5" aria-labelledby="relatedServicesHeading">
        <h2 id="relatedServicesHeading" class="heading-blush-bg text-center mb-4">Related Services</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="card shadow" style="background-color: var(--color-champers); border: 2px solid var(--color-gold); border-radius: 12px;">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
              <h3 class="text-gold mb-3">Corporate Events</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal">Corporate events crafted to honour people, purpose, and place.</p>
